</blockquote><br />\n自己做莊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>哪有本事做莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5e464a10548fbcd3580c0cf307298247f895a0","tid":296532,"uid":72399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:44:49.000Z","msg":"十幾歲就有十幾萬可以輸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6d01bf4263918127d9e3d57968a6c7d5f5ab0f","tid":296532,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:46:08.000Z","msg":"錢都未識搵有十幾皮輸，算唔錯😂😂😂"},{"pid":"93532de12e391b026954af16ea1f5a802c7399a0","tid":296532,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:47:00.000Z","msg":"巴打收手la<br />\n個個都以為自己贏，贏到一早執曬la d莊家<br />\n真係贏，唔係內幕就計埋d mit 數"},{"pid":"41e8ec93078957fb83777fd8b30bc8187955d500","tid":296532,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:50:10.000Z","msg":"有賭未為輸 十幾萬都唔追番佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab46abc0e1f45897f0622150e63314332dddfa8a","tid":296532,"uid":123699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:45:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十幾歲就有十幾萬可以輸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夾夾埋埋，讀書個陣三四年前有係日本代購叫揾到啲(個期)"},{"pid":"709b76a72134c3bd5cda469119ea96a374be41dd","tid":296532,"uid":123699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:54:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打收手la<br />\n個個都以為自己贏，贏到一早執曬la d莊家<br />\n真係贏，唔係內幕就計埋d mit 數</blockquote><br />\n賭左咁耐，真係唔知有無內幕喎。不過多謝ching好言相勸"},{"pid":"891a11ba41ee886fd93e0f081e9defc7c82df79e","tid":296532,"uid":123699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:02:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有賭未為輸 十幾萬都唔追番佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n單頭買一注十萬都有機會追到嘅。首先，呢一刻我無lol。第二，有我都不會一炮轟落去，會攞黎做其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf8e42c66bb8a714fecab646fc0a949a8558fbe","tid":296532,"uid":42187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:06:15.000Z","msg":"10幾萬咁少 ....."},{"pid":"9614652dea81cfd8839b58a7a520bdda7be41dec","tid":296532,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:12:26.000Z","msg":"12歲開始賭<br />\n一開始係uwants賭分<br />\n輸曬就洗版拎分再賭<br />\n高中就開始叫fd幫手買<br />\n到宜家四大聯賽差唔多場場賭足，每個禮拜18場馬都唔會缺席<br />\n<br />\n但都無輸10萬咁多，我諗計埋其實都係打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e6d1d39a0fd92fa4c5329c1ef8fd02c8a13cd5","tid":296532,"uid":123699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:03:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10幾萬咁少 .....</blockquote><br />\n賭左三年幾左右，我覺得唔算少了"},{"pid":"3477ae765811f2e9ff1c75aebee36c0a250589e3","tid":296532,"uid":123699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:04:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>12歲開始賭<br />\n一開始係uwants賭分<br />\n輸曬就洗版拎分再賭<br />\n高中就開始叫fd幫手買<br />\n到宜家四大聯賽差唔多場場賭足，每個禮拜18場馬都唔會缺席<br />\n<br />\n但都無輸10萬咁多，我諗計埋其實都係打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n望早脫苦海"},{"pid":"5917ef576642d152b4708c015095417f1f5cc45f","tid":296532,"uid":67010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:12:13.000Z","msg":"做球員真係好賺睇轉會費就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然要踢出身價 但唔擔保佢地有冇打假啦<br />\n但我覺得場場都仲會有D球員係收到通知做假<br />\n你睇澳職 就知....其他次級更加唔洗講<br />\n大聯賽都有 只係冇咁明顯姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申戒左賭 睇住比數上上落落真係好正"},{"pid":"b12b387f2f0c9ca3f65e586239e266e04686a49d","tid":296532,"uid":123699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:55:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做球員真係好賺睇轉會費就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然要踢出身價 但唔擔保佢地有冇打假啦<br />\n但我覺得場場都仲會有D球員係收到通知做假<br />\n你睇澳職 就知....其他次級更加唔洗講<br />\n大聯賽都有 只係冇咁明顯姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申戒左賭 睇住比數上上落落真係好正</blockquote><br />\n求戒賭教學，我覺得自己一個人好難戒。有女易啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至少有啲寄托有啲目標，唔會咁易亂fing 錢 利申單身狗"},{"pid":"902e38cce08054047dfa65324ab1056a45aa84b9","tid":296532,"uid":67010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做球員真係好賺睇轉會費就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然要踢出身價 但唔擔保佢地有冇打假啦<br />\n但我覺得場場都仲會有D球員係收到通知做假<br />\n你睇澳職 就知....其他次級更加唔洗講<br />\n大聯賽都有 只係冇咁明顯姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申戒左賭 睇住比數上上落落真係好正</blockquote><br />\n求戒賭教學，我覺得自己一個人好難戒。有女易啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至少有啲寄托有啲目標，唔會咁易亂fing 錢 利申單身狗</blockquote><br />\n我都係一個人 搵緊工返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係靠唔睇波戒 但係有留意比數咁 <br />\n<br />\n除非真係好想睇先會睇<br />\n我係靠打機消磨時間 <br />\n一到睇波晚上呢D睇波時間都係打機 唔差在講打咩啦<br />\n英雄聯盟 你應該都識既<br />\n 我睇比賽就當睇場波咁樣過日子<br />\n之後竟然咁就唔賭戒左了 仲有因爲我比較少出街所以冇入錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家都睇緊比呀呢個時間"}]}